South Africans to Demonstrate After Police Kill Protester, Times Reports

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-04-18T05:17:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-18/south-africans-to-demonstrate-after-police-kill-protester-times-reports.html
Thousands of people are expected to
demonstrate in the central South African town of Ficksburg today
when six policemen appear in court over the death of Andries
Tatane, who died in a protest last week, Johannesburg’s Times
newspaper reported.  Tatane’s death was captured by television cameras, which
showed him being beaten by policemen.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
